---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Canton Fair Guide"
  description="Canton Fair preparation for overseas buyers: registration, phases, hotels, product categories, and supplier follow-up."
  canonical="/canton-fair/"
>
  <section class="content-page">
    <div class="page-header">
      <span class="eyebrow">Canton Fair Guide</span>
      <h1>Prepare for the Canton Fair like a serious buyer.</h1>
      <p>
        Build a focused trip plan before arriving in Guangzhou: know the phase, pick the right hotel area, prepare
        supplier questions, and create a follow-up system.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="content-grid">
      <div class="prose">
        <h2>Core topics</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Canton Fair phases and product categories</li>
          <li>Buyer badge registration and invitation letter basics</li>
          <li>Where to stay in Guangzhou during the fair</li>
          <li>How to compare suppliers after booth meetings</li>
          <li>What to do before visiting factories after the fair</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Helpful resources for buyers</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Canton Fair buyer checklist before you travel</li>
          <li>Guangzhou market route planning tips</li>
          <li>Supplier comparison notes for post-fair follow-up</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <aside class="sidebar">
        <div class="notice-box">
          <h2>First visit tip</h2>
          <p>Confirm your phase and hotel area before booking flights so your fair days stay focused and efficient.</p>
          <a class="button secondary" href="/blog/canton-fair-first-time-buyer-guide/">Read buyer guide</a>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
